OL,11,G2000 The Hotel Inspector
OL,12,     FAward-winning hotelier and leading
OL,13,     Fbusiness guru Alex Polizzi, is on
OL,14,     Fa quest to turn badly run hotels
OL,15,     Finto profitable ventures. Alex
OL,16,     Fcast fresh eyes over a number of
OL,17,     Ffading hotels.
